<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.catholiceducation.org/articles/persecution/pch0151.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.catholiceducation.org/articles/persecution/pch0151.htm" rel="nofollow">Lord Have Mercy: A review of God is Not Great: How Religion Poisons Everything</a> by Ross Douthat</li>
<li id="cite_note-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.eurekastreet.com.au/article.aspx?aeid=2955" class="external text" title="http://www.eurekastreet.com.au/article.aspx?aeid=2955" rel="nofollow">Frank Brennan answers atheist manifestos</a>, retrieved <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2007-06-01"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="06-01"><a href="/wiki/June_01" title="June 01" class="mw-redirect">June 01</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2007" title="2007">2007</a></span>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-21"><b><a href="#cite_ref-21" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://ap.google.com/article/ALeqM5gIKp6SMKuAR1cD8M3gd3OePuyDbgD8S6HC081" class="external text" title="http://ap.google.com/article/ALeqM5gIKp6SMKuAR1cD8M3gd3OePuyDbgD8S6HC081" rel="nofollow">Associated Press</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-22"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.amazon.com/dp/0446579807" class="external text" title="http://www.amazon.com/dp/0446579807" rel="nofollow">Amazon.com book page - search for sales rank for current position</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-23"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/03/books/bestseller/0603besthardnonfiction.html" class="external text" title="http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/03/books/bestseller/0603besthardnonfiction.html" rel="nofollow">New York Times Bestseller list</a></li>
